<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 出租汽车：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>take a taxi</strong> to the station
乘出租汽车到车站</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go home <strong>by taxi</strong>
乘出租汽车回家</p></div></div>